title: Crop Circle Corn Maze
description:
Written by Jon Bershad
Starring: Dan Hodapp, Lisa Kleinman, Zack Phillips, Avery Monsen, Kelly Hudson, Jon Bershad, Jonathan Marballi.

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, October 21, 2013.

Filmed by Jocelyne Jo Roueiheb and Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
